#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:5
msgid "Tool System"
msgstr "工具系统"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:7
msgid "Tools are accessed from the :ref:`Toolbar <ui-region-toolbar>`,"
msgstr "可以从 :ref:`工具栏 <ui-region-toolbar>` 中选择工具 ,"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:9
msgid ""
"This is a general introduction to tools, individual tools have their own "
"documentation."
msgstr "这只是一般性的工具介绍，每个工具有自己的文档说明。"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:11
msgid "There can only be one active tool which is stored for each space & mode."
msgstr "每个空间&模式只能有一个活动工具。"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:13
msgid ""
"Tools may set their own keys which override other keys although typically "
"they use the :kbd:`LMB`, sometimes with modifier keys. *Key-maps can be "
"edited from the preferences.*"
msgstr ""
"尽管通常是用 :kbd:`LMB` 打开，有时也会用到组合快捷键，但其实每个工具都可以通过"
"覆盖其他按键而拥有自己的快捷键。 *键位映射可在偏好设置中修改。*"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:17
msgid ""
"Some tools define gizmos (*Shear* and *Spin* for example) to help control the "
"tool."
msgstr "有些工具有操纵杆（比如 *切变* 和 *旋绕*）以协助使用。"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:23
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "工具栏"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:28
msgid "Button with pop-up menu indicator."
msgstr "弹出菜单指示按钮。"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:30
msgid ""
"The Toolbar shows buttons for each tool. For tool buttons which have an small "
"triangle in bottom right corner will reveal a pop-up menu when you :kbd:`LMB` "
"drag so that you can select other tools of the same group."
msgstr ""
"工具栏显示每个工具按钮，工具按钮的右下角有一个小的三角形，使用 :kbd:`LMB` 拖拽"
"可以弹出一个菜单，菜单包含了同一组类型的工具。"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:34
msgid ""
"Hovering your cursor over a tool for a short time shows it's name, keep it "
"longer to show the full tooltip."
msgstr "把鼠标放在工具上面一会儿，会显示工具的名称、快捷键等。"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:36
msgid ""
"Expand the Toolbar to show icons on two columns instead of one or even more "
"to show icons with titles."
msgstr "拉伸工具栏显示两行或者带名称的图标。"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:40
msgid "Properties"
msgstr "属性"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:42
msgid "Tools can have their own settings, these are available multiple place:"
msgstr "每个工具都有自己的设置，并在多个地方："

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:44
msgid "The :menuselection:`Sidebar --> Tools --> Active Tool` panel."
msgstr ":menuselection:`侧栏 --> 工具 --> 活动工具` 面板。"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:45
msgid "The *Active Tool* tab in the Properties editor."
msgstr "属性编辑器的 *活动工具* 选项卡。"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:46
msgid "The *Tool Settings* region."
msgstr "*工具设置* 区块。"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:50
msgid "Switching Tools"
msgstr "切换工具"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:52
msgid ""
"Keyboard tool switching is not enabled by default, set the key-map "
"preference :ref:`keymap-blender_default-spacebar_action` to *Tools*. Then you "
"can be used as a modifier key (similar to pressing :kbd:`Ctrl` or :kbd:"
"`Shift`)."
msgstr ""
"切换工具默认没有快捷键, 给工具设置键盘映射 :ref:`keymap-blender_default-"
"spacebar_action` 。 你可以添加组合键来实现工具的切换 ( 类似于按 :kbd:`Ctrl` "
"或 :kbd:`Shift`)。"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:56
msgid ""
":kbd:`Spacebar-T` for Transform, :kbd:`Spacebar-D` for Annotate, :kbd:"
"`Spacebar-M` for measure, etc."
msgstr ""
"你可以使用组合快捷键的方式来切换工具。比如：\n"
":kbd:`Spacebar-T` 用于形变, :kbd:`Spacebar-D` 用于标注, :kbd:`Spacebar-M` 用于"
"度量等。"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:58
msgid "*The accelerator keys are displayed in the tooltip.*"
msgstr "*加速键在工具提示中显示。*"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:62
msgid "Cycling Tools"
msgstr "循环工具"

#: ../../manual/interface/tool_system.rst:64
msgid ""
"If you bind a key to a tool which is part of a group, you can enable the "
"*Cycle* option in the keymap editor, successive presses cycles through tools "
"in that group."
msgstr ""
"如果绑定一组工具至同一个快捷键，则可以在键盘映射编辑器中启用“ 循环”选项，连续"
"按下该组中的工具。"
